===================================================================
                  OSYSO COMMAND STATIONS CHEAT SHEET              
===================================================================

[ PRE-INSTALLATION WIREGUARD CONFIG PIPELINE ]
  1. Create secure key directory:
     sudo mkdir -p /mnt/etc/wireguard && sudo chmod 700 /mnt/etc/wireguard
  2. Generate mesh keypair:
     cd /mnt/etc/wireguard && wg genkey | sudo tee private_key | wg pubkey | sudo tee public_key
  3. Secure token access:
     sudo chmod 600 private_key public_key

[ WORKSPACE CONTROL HUB ]
  - Super + 1        : Jump to OVERSOUL (Dashboard & Operations Platform)
  - Super + 2        : Jump to DEVOPS (Isolated Sandbox Environment)
  - Super + 3        : Jump to EDITOR (School Vault & Graphic Station)
  - Super + Space    : Unified App Launcher / Shell Command Prompt
  - Super + Enter    : Quick-draw a fresh Kitty Terminal Station
  - Super + Shift + C: Live Reload Whole Desktop Aesthetic Layout

[ PYPRLAND QUICK-DRAW SIDE PANELS ]
  - Super + ~ (Grave): Toggle Hidden Top Drop-Down System Terminal
  - Super + D        : Toggle Hidden Right-Edge Social Panel (Discord)

[ DYNAMIC ENVIRONMENT OVERRIDES ]
  - set-node         : Inject Node.js 22, TypeScript, and Vite into Sandbox
  - set-ml           : Launch Python Machine Learning Pipeline Matrix
  - set-web          : Activate Python Web Stack, Postgres, and Redis Server
  - allow            : Authorize directory sandbox clearance profile

[ WIREGUARD MESH LIFELINE ]
  - vpn-stat         : View active peer status updates and ping latency
  - vpn-up / down    : Force connect or drop secure network infrastructure

